 Jada P and Wizkid Wizkid’s baby mama, Jada Pollock has opened up on how she and Afrobeat specialist, Wizkid crossed paths. The artist manager said she met the award-winning artiste back in 2012 when she was still managing R&B superstar, Chris Bown. She added that it has been an incredible journey and she is blessed to have work with a lot of talented artistes, including Wizkid. Jada also added that she’s evolving in her line of duty and that’s something she’s happy about. View this post on Instagram A post shared by JADA ☄️ (@__jada.p)